PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of certain persons as directors of the Board of Directors of the Canadian National Railway Company to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective March 29, 1995. (J.V. RAYMOND CYR, Montreal, Quebec, in the place of Bernard A. Roy, who has resigned; and CEDRIC E. RITCHIE, Don Mills, Ontario, in the place of Francis J. Ryan, who has resigned)
